The paper proposes a new method for network embedding, which is a popular topic in machine learning and data mining. The paper focuses on unsupervised homogeneous network embedding, which is a subfield of network embedding. The paper also mentions downstream machine learning tasks such as network reconstruction, link prediction, and node classification, which are common tasks in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
